data.description: Welcome to this stunning 3 bedroom, 3 bath property situated on over 10 acres, boasting breathtaking 360-degree mountain views and spectacular sunsets. Built with all steel construction, this home offers durability and elegance. Enjoy abundant natural light through the French doors in the 900 sq foot living room and owner's suite. The extra-large owner's suite features a spa for ultimate relaxation. Wood laminate floors add warmth throughout. Additionally, there is an 18 x 40 greenhouse and a 20 x 40 steel construction workshop. This meticulously maintained home showcases the owner's pride. The well-appointed kitchen showcases silestone countertops. Outside, a large paved patio awaits your personal touch. With a 4-car garage, this property truly has it all.
